commit.message:
xtensa-config.h (XSHAL_USE_ABSOLUTE_LITERALS, [...]): New.

2004-10-07  Bob Wilson  <bob.wilson@acm.org>
        * xtensa-config.h (XSHAL_USE_ABSOLUTE_LITERALS,
        XCHAL_HAVE_PREDICTED_BRANCHES, XCHAL_INST_FETCH_WIDTH): New.

From-SVN: r88727
